      "body" : "From the 4.3 docs: <i>the Servlet container will typically write an HTML error page therefore making the use of a <code>reason</code> unsuitable for REST APIs. For such cases it is preferable to use a <code>ResponseEntity</code> as a return type and avoid the use of <code>ResponseStatus</code> altogether</i>"
