    "answer_id" : 2067043,
    "question_id" : 2066946,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>Since Spring 3.0 you also can throw an Exception declared with <a href=\"http://static.springsource.org/spring/docs/3.0.x/javadoc-api/org/springframework/web/bind/annotation/ResponseStatus.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>@ResponseStatus</code></a> annotation:</p>\n\n<pre><code>@ResponseStatus(value = HttpStatus.NOT_FOUND)\npublic class ResourceNotFoundException extends RuntimeException {\n    ...\n}\n\n@Controller\npublic class SomeController {\n    @RequestMapping.....\n    public void handleCall() {\n        if (isFound()) {\n            // whatever\n        }\n        else {\n            throw new ResourceNotFoundException(); \n        }\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
