      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "you have mapped exceptions of type Exception(and subclasses) with a 404 status code. Did you ever think there are internal server errors? How do you plan to handle those in your GlobalControllerExceptionHandler?"
    }, {
      "owner" : {
        "account_id" : 225072,
