      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "If you are using Sentry or similar in PROD, and don&#39;t want to spam it with errors that are no actual errors, this solution is much better compared to the one using exceptions for this non-exceptional situation."
    }, {
      "owner" : {
        "account_id" : 74886,
