    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 6,
    "last_activity_date" : 1450256465,
    "creation_date" : 1450256465,
    "answer_id" : 34307704,
    "question_id" : 2066946,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I'd recommend throwing <strong>HttpClientErrorException</strong>, like this</p>\n\n<pre><code>@RequestMapping(value = \"/sample/\")\npublic void sample() {\n    if (somethingIsWrong()) {\n        throw new HttpClientErrorException(HttpStatus.NOT_FOUND);\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>You must remember that this can be done only before anything is written to servlet output stream.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "comments" : [ {
      "owner" : {
